The paper proposes a novel approach for vocabulary reuse in Linked Open Data by exploiting information on how other data providers use RDF types and properties. This involves the use of machine learning algorithms and evaluation metrics commonly used in the fields of artificial intelligence, databases, information retrieval, software engineering, and social networks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.SI, and cs.SE.
